sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_snc_meetnowapp_interaction</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>interaction_ical</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {

	if (current.date_of_interaction.changes() || current.assigned_to.changes()) {
		if (!current.date_of_interaction.nil() && !current.assigned_to.nil()) {
			gs.eventQueue("x_snc_meetnowapp.interaction.cal.notify", current, current.assigned_to, previous.assigned_to);
	    }

	   // Remove from previous assigned to, due to assigned_to changing
		if (!previous.assigned_to.nil()) {
			if (!current.assigned_to.nil() && current.assigned_to.changes() && (!previous.date_of_interaction.nil())) {
				gs.eventQueue("x_snc_meetnowapp.interaction.cal.remove", current, current.assigned_to, previous.assigned_to);
			}
	   }
		
	   // Remove old calendar from current assigned to, due to date changing
	   else if (!current.assigned_to.nil()) {
		   if ((current.date_of_interaction.changes() && !previous.date_of_interaction.nil())) {
			   gs.eventQueue("x_snc_meetnowapp.interaction.cal.remove", current, current.assigned_to, current.assigned_to);
		   }
	   }
	}
	
	// If status set to active then add to calendar
	else if (current.u_status.getAttribute(active) === "Active") {
		gs.eventQueue("x_snc_meetnowapp.interaction.cal.notify", current, current.assigned_to, previous.assigned_to);
	}
	
	// If status set to cancelled then remove from calendar
	else if (current.u_status.getAttribute(canceldecline) === "Cancelled/Declined") {
		gs.eventQueue("x_snc_meetnowapp.interaction.cal.notify", current, current.assigned_to, previous.assigned_to);
	}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>james.birch</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-06-09 16:29:10</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>62f60353fd3712007f442d2777314293</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>interaction_ical</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="MeetNowApp" source="x_snc_meetnowapp">34a6d5dffd7312007f442d2777314260</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="MeetNowApp">34a6d5dffd7312007f442d2777314260</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_62f60353fd3712007f442d2777314293</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>james.birch</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-06-10 09:02:56</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=62f60353fd3712007f442d2777314293"/></record_update>

	var value = current.getValue('date_of_interaction');
	if(!value) {
		return true;  // empty fields are still valid dates

	// We "should" have the global date format defined always defined. but there's always that edge case...
	if(typeof g_user_date_time_format !== 'undefined')

	// if we don't have that defined, we can always try guessing
	return parseDate(value) !== null;
	
	
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>jaren.liu</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-06-09 18:12:50</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>034e139bfd3712007f442d27773142de</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Date of Interaction Validation Check</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="MeetNowApp" source="x_snc_meetnowapp">34a6d5dffd7312007f442d2777314260</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="MeetNowApp">34a6d5dffd7312007f442d2777314260</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_034e139bfd3712007f442d27773142de</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>jaren.liu</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-06-09 18:18:45</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=034e139bfd3712007f442d27773142de"/></record_update>
